---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import StructuredData from '../components/StructuredData.astro';
import ContactInfo from '../components/ContactInfo.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Websites for Tradies NZ | Get Found on Google | YourHQ"
  description="Professional websites for NZ electricians, plumbers, builders & painters. Built in 5 days. No Wix homework. You talk for 15 minutes—we do the rest. From $497 (Founding Offer)."
>
  <StructuredData slot="head" />

  <!-- Announcement Bar -->
  <div class="bg-signal text-white text-center py-3 px-4 text-sm font-mono tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-white/10">
    Founding Member Offer (Ends March 31, 2026): $497.50 Setup (50% Off) + $149/mo Locked for Life — 26 Spots | Code: FOUNDING26
  </div>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="relative pt-20 pb-24 md:pt-32 md:pb-40 border-b border-carbon bg-[size:40px_40px] bg-grid-pattern">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

          <div class="max-w-5xl">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 border border-carbon bg-white shadow-hard-sm mb-8">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-signal rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">FOR ELECTRICIANS • PLUMBERS • BUILDERS • PAINTERS</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Headline -->
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
              Stop Losing Jobs to Blokes Who <span class="text-signal">Just Show Up on Google.</span>
            </h1>

            <!-- Subhead -->
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-carbon/90 max-w-3xl mb-8">
              You can have 15 years' experience and a 4.8-star reputation — but when someone searches "electrician near me", Google decides who gets the call.
            </p>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
              Done-for-you websites for Kiwi tradies — built in 5 days. No Wix. No homework. One 15-minute chat. We do the rest.
            </p>

            <!-- CTAs -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="#offer" class="bg-signal text-white px-8 py-4 text-center border border-carbon shadow-hard hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[2px] transition-all font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                Claim the Founding Deal (50% Off)
              </a>
              <a href="#process" class="bg-white text-carbon px-8 py-4 text-center border border-carbon shadow-hard-sm hover:shadow-none hover:translate-y-[2px] transition-all font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                See How It Works
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUSTED BY NZ TRADIES -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <p class="text-center text-sm font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8">Trusted by NZ Tradies</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-10 md:gap-16">
          <img src="/carve-logo.png" alt="Carve" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300" />
          <img src="/johnsonandsons-logo.png" alt="Johnson and Sons" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 1: THE PROBLEM -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-6">
                You're Flat Out on the Tools. <br/>
                <span class="text-frangipani">So Why Does It Still Feel Like Money's Slipping Through?</span>
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-gray-300">
              <p>Here's what happens every day: Someone needs a tradie. They grab their phone and search: "[trade] + near me" or "[trade] + [suburb]".</p>
              <p>Google shows a short list. They call the one that looks legit.</p>
              <p>If your online presence is messy — or you're not showing up at all — you don't even get a chance.</p>

              <!-- Callout -->
              <div class="bg-white/10 p-8 border border-white/20 mt-8">
                <p class="text-signal font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-2">Most Customers Trust a Website More Than Social Media</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">When someone's choosing between you and another tradie, they Google both names. One of you looks established. One of you looks like a risk. <br/><br/><strong class="text-white">Which one are you?</strong></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: OLD MATE DAVE TEST -->
    <section class="bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">

            <!-- Left: Visual -->
            <div class="bg-white border-r border-carbon p-12 md:p-24 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[400px]">
              <div class="relative w-full aspect-square border-2 border-carbon overflow-hidden bg-gray-50 shadow-hard-sm group">
                <img src="/tradie-phone.webp" alt="Tradie checking phone on job site" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" />
                <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-full h-full border border-signal -z-10"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: The Content -->
            <div class="p-8 md:p-24 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">
                Be Honest: Would You Hire a Tradie With <span class="text-signal">No Website?</span>
              </h2>

              <div class="prose text-carbon space-y-6 text-lg">
                <p>Even if Dave recommends a plumber, you're still going to Google them first. If you find: no website, an outdated one, or a dodgy page from years ago …you hesitate.</p>
                <p>Your customers are doing the same thing to you. Right now.</p>

                <div class="py-6 border-t border-carbon/20 mt-6">
                    <p class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Total time from you: one 15-minute phone call.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: THE PROCESS -->
    <section id="process" class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
               <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight sticky top-24">
                Built in 5 Days.<br/>
                Zero Homework.<br/>
                <span class="text-gray-400">(Seriously.)</span>
              </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-0">
              <!-- Step 1 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 pb-16 border-l border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-signal border-4 border-white"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-signal mb-2 block">STEP 01</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Drive-Home Interview (15 mins)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-xl">
                    Call us for a quick chat while you're driving home (or between jobs). Hands-free, records automatically, captures everything we need. No forms. No typing. No meetings.
                  </p>
                  <span class="inline-block bg-paper px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold border border-carbon/20">NO WIXING REQUIRED</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 2 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 pb-16 border-l border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-carbon border-4 border-white"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-carbon mb-2 block">STEP 02</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">We Do the Digging (0 mins)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-xl">
                    We pull photos, reviews, logos, and details from your socials and Google — so you don't have to chase files.
                  </p>
                  <span class="inline-block bg-paper px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold border border-carbon/20">WE DO THE DIGGING</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 3 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 pb-16 border-l border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-hibiscus border-4 border-white"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-hibiscus mb-2 block">STEP 03</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Factory Build (5 Days)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 max-w-xl">
                    We build your site — structure, copy, design, mobile, SEO basics — the whole lot. Fast-loading. Modern. Built to convert.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Step 4 -->
              <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 border-l border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
                <div class="absolute -left-3 top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-frangipani border-4 border-white"></div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-frangipani mb-2 block">STEP 04</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Preview on Day 5 (Love it / Fix it / Refund it)</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2 max-w-xl">
                    We send a private preview link. Want tweaks? We sort them. Don't love it? Full refund of your setup fee (minus ~3% processing + any domain costs).
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: THE MATH -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-carbon p-8 md:p-12 shadow-hard">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-8">
                    The Math That <span class="text-signal">Matters</span>
                </h2>

                <p class="text-lg text-carbon/90 text-center mb-8">
                    You don't need 100 new leads. You need the right people to find you — and trust you — when they're ready to spend.
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-carbon/90 border-b-2 border-dashed border-gray-200 pb-8 mb-8">
                    <ul class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm md:text-base">
                        <li class="flex justify-between">
                            <span>Average job value (varies, but often):</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">$1,000–$5,000</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between items-center text-signal font-bold">
                            <span>Even one extra job a month:</span>
                            <span>$12k–$60k/yr</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between text-gray-500">
                            <span>YourHQ cost (Launch):</span>
                            <span>$995 setup + $149/mo</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center space-y-6">
                    <p class="text-xl font-bold">Payback: one decent job can cover the whole first year.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        We can't promise you'll rank #1 overnight — it depends on your area and competition. But we build sites that load fast, look legit, and help you show up more clearly on Google.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: GET FOUND ON GOOGLE MAPS -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8">
                Most Tradie Work Starts on Google Maps. <br/>
                <span class="text-signal">Are You Even On There?</span>
              </h2>

              <div class="prose text-carbon space-y-6 text-lg">
                <p>Someone needs a tradie. They search <strong>"electrician near me."</strong> Google shows the map pack — usually 3 businesses. If you're not in that mix, you're invisible.</p>

                <div class="py-6 border-t border-carbon/20 mt-6">
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-2xl mb-4">We put you on the map. Literally.</p>
                    <p>We set up (or tidy up) your Google Maps listing and link it properly to your website — so when people search in your area, you show up like a real business.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="bg-paper p-8 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard">

                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Claim & verify your Google Maps listing (where needed)</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Write your business description</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Upload job photos</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Set your service areas</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Link to your website</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
                        <span class="font-medium">Basic optimisation so it actually works for you</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-paper border-b border-carbon">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-16 text-center">
          Real Tradies. <span class="text-signal">Real Speed.</span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Main Feature Testimonial -->
        <div class="bg-paper text-carbon p-8 md:p-12 border-l-8 border-signal relative shadow-hard-white mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <span class="text-6xl text-gray-200 font-serif absolute top-4 left-4 -z-10">"</span>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed italic relative z-10">
                "While I was still figuring out Google Drive, Lian had already pulled images from our Facebook and had a draft site ready. My mates reckon it's banging."
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between mt-8 border-t border-carbon/10 pt-6 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-lg">Reuben, Johnson & Sons</p>
                    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Commercial Builder</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-signal">
                    <span>✓ Fast Turnaround</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
                    <span>✓ Zero Homework</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Extra Proof -->
        <div class="bg-paper text-carbon p-8 border-l-8 border-frangipani relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
              "Smooth, easy and stress-free — with a clean professional outcome."
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <p class="font-extrabold">Brad, Carve Earthworks</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Owner Operator</p>
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: WHY WE EXIST -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-6">Based in Whangārei. Built for Tradies Who Don't Have Time for This Stuff.</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Half of NZ small businesses still don't have a website. Not because they're lazy — because they're busy.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                DIY tools take weeks of after-hours stress. Agencies charge $10–15k and move slow. We built YourHQ for tradies who just want it sorted: fast build, no homework, ongoing support, and a website that doesn't rot.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: FAQ (YEAH, BUT...) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-12 text-center">
            Yeah, <span class="text-signal">But...</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- FAQ 1 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-signal p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"I'm already fully booked. Why do I need a website?"</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                So you can choose better work — not just more work. A good site helps you look premium, attract higher-quality enquiries, and charge accordingly.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 2 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-hibiscus p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"I don't have time for this."</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                You don't need time. Total input from you: one 15-minute call. We handle the rest.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 3 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-frangipani p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"My nephew can build me one for free."</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Will he be around when it breaks? Will he update it? Will he keep it secure and fast? Free websites often get expensive later.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 4 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-signal p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"Websites are expensive."</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Some agencies charge $10–15k and disappear. We charge $995 + GST and stay on as caretakers.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 5 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-hibiscus p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"Will this help me show up on Google Maps?"</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Yes — we set up or optimise your Google Maps listing and connect it properly to your site. Results vary by area, but most businesses start seeing improvement over time as Google re-indexes.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 6 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-frangipani p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"I already have a Google listing but it's a mess. Can you fix it?"</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                Yes. If it's claimed, we optimise it. If it's unclaimed, we help get it sorted.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ 7 -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-signal p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-carbon">"How do I get more Google reviews?"</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                On Growth, we include a review collection system. On Launch, we'll still point you in the right direction to make it easy for customers to leave reviews.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: PRICING WITH FOUNDING MEMBER OFFER -->
    <section id="offer" class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

          <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
             <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mb-4">Founding Member Offer <span class="text-signal">(Ends March 31, 2026)</span></h2>
             <p class="text-xl text-signal font-bold">Launch Package: $497.50 setup (50% off) + $149/mo locked for life</p>
             <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2">26 spots only | Use code: FOUNDING26</p>
