                        FOUNDING26
                    </div>
                </div>

                <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 flex-1">
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal">✓</span> 5-page professional website</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-signal">✓</span> 15-minute drive-home interview (no homework)</li>
